## Security Features

- **Helmet** — Sets 15+ HTTP security headers
- **Rate Limiting** — 100 req/15min (API), 10 req/15min (auth)  
- **Mongo Sanitize** — Prevents `$gt`, `$where` injection
- **XSS Clean** — Strips `<script>` tags from inputs
- **CORS** — Locked to frontend URL only
- **JWT** — 7-day expiry, bcrypt-12 password hashing
- **Centralized Errors** — Safe messages in production (no stack traces)
